{"tid":1417750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「和理非」「文宣」係時候要強調五大訴求！!","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:52:42.000Z","uid":217430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32aee0a937085470862b0bb4764e71bef7534f18","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"各位前線勇武義士，辛苦你地了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝早柒婆係記者會度，完全唔提五大訴求，成個重點都係暴力同破壞經濟。<br />\n<br />\n而且來緊每日警方都會有記者會。好明顯，柒婆好想不停地幫市民洗腦：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">暴徒！破壞經濟！</span></span><br />\n既然係噤，我地就來個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">反洗腦</span></span>！「和理非」、「文宣」全面進場！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地有必要再次強調整個活動既主軸：五大訴求！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n隨著整個運動既發展，每個訴求都有各自最根本，背後既原因。大家遊行、做文宣不防可以畫公仔畫出腸，講多句「歇後語」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n我要真雙普選     拒絕中央任命<br />\n撒回送中惡法     拒絕壽終正寢<br />\n獨立調查黑警     拒絕軍警政府<br />\n釋放被補義士     拒絕政治檢控<br />\n取消暴動定性     拒絕歪曲事實</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我將真普選排第一，係因為呢個係五大訴求中最重要的。我地要徹底改變整個制度，避免以後再有惡法重臨立法會。<br />\n<br />\n大家要緊記初心，唔好被仇恨支配。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7088ca7ae84f17511a6f9e8208a3384c0bf959","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"767025ec5da047962dc6f3e4812c97cdd0e5dac6","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eabebb973fa8ce421268bd6c1884dfe50bebfbc","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c609edd6639a55ad1fd12da2cd3e6ec6f95c9bd5","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:10:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61eeadc42381ec314be1e02cbe30f426158a3f62","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:11:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3fa427da40110606beaafd8289270e3f908b755","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:52:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e78320feb766d641445aa1a2d8ef0fe17f013a9e","tid":1417750,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}